Text: Syd Barret is a psychoactive, musical genius.  David Gilmore is a egocentric hack.  All you pink floyd fans who own dark side of the moon, the wall and wish u were here, take note: UMMA GUMMA, THE MADCAP LAUGHS, OPEL, SAUCER FULL OF SECRETS, OBSCURED BY CLOUDS, BARRETT.  Yours truly, Pinki Tuscaderro.
